  <lyrics>[V1]
 Kaypi kashan Señor Jesús,
 Tükuy kusikunchej Paywanña kaspa.
 Kaypi kashan Señor Jesús,
 Aleluya, Diosninchej noqanchejwan.
 
[V2]
 Biblianejta Señor Jesús
 Tukuy wawasninman parlaykuwanchej.
 Leenachej, oranachej,
 Aleluya, Diosninchej noqanchejwan.
 
[V3]
 Willamuna Palabranta,
 Chirispipis, q’oñispipis purispa,
 Willaraspa Palabranta.
 Aleluya, Diosninchej noqanchejwan.
 
</lyrics></song>